## 1. Exact File Paths and Line Numbers Where "Open", "Rename", "Delete" Buttons Are Defined

All three buttons are defined in a single file:

**File:** `/home/glompy/Desktop/ASTROCYTECH/Agent_X/ui/src/App.jsx`

| Button | Line | Code |
|--------|------|------|
| **Open** | **Line 223** | `<button className="btn btn-open" onClick={() => { onSelect(s); onClose(); }}>Open</button>` |
| **Rename** | **Line 224** | `<button className="btn btn-rename" onClick={() => startRename(s)}>Rename</button>` |
| **Delete** | **Line 225** | `<button className="btn btn-delete" onClick={() => handleDelete(s.run_id)}>Delete</button>` |

There is also a secondary **Delete** confirmation button at **Line 248**:
```jsx
<button className="btn btn-delete" onClick={confirmDelete}>Delete</button>
```

These all reside inside the `SessionModal` function component (lines 111-276), which is rendered as a modal overlay triggered by the "Session > Open Session..." menu item (line 13, menu id `openSession`) or by the keyboard shortcut `Ctrl+O` (line 498).

